    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've seriously gotta see this beauty in person. It\u2019s in absolutely incredible shape\u2014honestly, it looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it really shows. No scratches, no dings, just pure perfection inside and out. If you're looking for a ride that's been loved and is ready for a new home, this is the one! Shoot me a message and come take it for a spin!",
