    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a superlative example of high-revving, naturally aspirated engineering. The S54 straight-six engine exhibits flawless harmonic balance, with the Vanos system recently serviced to ensure optimal variable valve timing. Power is delivered through a crisp Getrag six-speed manual transmission to a limited-slip differential, providing exceptional mechanical grip and exit speeds. The chassis is structurally sound with a reinforced rear subframe, and the suspension geometry remains factory-precise, offering the tactile feedback and telepathic turn-in characteristic of a true homologation-bred icon. Every bushing, seal, and fluid line reflects a no-expense-spared maintenance philosophy, resulting in a vehicle that performs exactly as it did when it left Regensburg.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_11_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_11",
      "description": "Mint condition. Single owner. Garage kept. No mechanical issues. Clean title. Service records available.",
      "price": 43500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
