      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 28
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_12_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_12",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true time capsule, preserved in showroom condition since day one. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish entirely free of swirl marks, stone chips, or parking lot imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains immaculate; the premium upholstery shows no signs of wear or creasing, and every switch, dial, and electronic feature functions with crisp precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having been strictly garage-kept and maintained with an open-checkbook policy at authorized service centers. The engine bay is clean enough to eat off of, and the undercarriage is free of corrosion. Offering a driving experience indistinguishable from a brand-new model, this car comes complete with all original keys, manuals, and a comprehensive service history. It is, quite simply, the finest example currently available on the market.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
