      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. This beauty has been pampered since day one\u2014always garaged and kept in truly pristine condition. It seriously looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! If you\u2019ve been looking for a ride that\u2019s been meticulously loved and cared for, you\u2019ve found it. Come take a look, you definitely won't be disappointed! \u2728",
      "price": 44900.0,
