    {
      "id": "sybil_13_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_13",
      "description": "Offered is a pristine FD3S Mazda RX-7, featuring the legendary 13B-REW sequential twin-turbocharged rotary powerplant. This example exhibits flawless sequential boost transition, indicating a vacuum system in peak operational health. The front-midship engine placement ensures a perfect 50/50 weight distribution, complemented by a factory-correct double-wishbone suspension that retains its original geometry and bushing integrity. The five-speed manual transmission engages with mechanical precision, and the limited-slip differential provides optimal torque bias under load. Verified compression across both rotors confirms the engine's internal health. This is a collector-grade specimen, free of aftermarket modifications and preserved in its original aerodynamic profile.",
